markets.title: Will repeal of the Jones Act becomes law before Jan 4, 2027?
markets.rules_primary: If repeal of the Jones Act becomes law before Jan 4, 2027, then the market resolves to Yes.
markets.rules_secondary:
This market will pay out if a bill becomes law that repeals the Jones Act, also known as the Merchant Marine Act of 1920 before January 4 2027 (the end of the 119th congress).
Additionally, if the general prohibition imposed by Jones Act on foreign-built, foreign-owned, or foreign-flagged vessels from engaging in coastwise trade within the United States is repealed or undone by newer legislation, the market will pay out.
markets.early_close_condition: This market will close and expire early if the event occurs.
